    <li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="dsq-comment-8526">
        <div id="dsq-comment-header-8526" class="dsq-comment-header">
            <cite id="dsq-cite-8526">
                <span id="dsq-author-user-8526">udp</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-8526" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-8526" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>A O(n^2Logn) solution<br />
1) Sort A[]<br />
2) Generate all pairs of two elements from A[]. Do following for every pair.<br />
&#8230;&#8230;a) Calculate sum of the current pair.<br />
&#8230;&#8230;b) Binary Search for sum minus sum of current pair. If the difference is found in array, then return true.<br />
3) Return false.</p>
</div>
        </div>

    <ul class="children">
    <li class="comment odd alt depth-2" id="dsq-comment-9160">
